login.if_you_are_retail_brand_or_business: If you are a retailer, brand or business, you can always sell on TikTok with any number of followers.
login.continue_login: Continue means you agree to the TikTok Shop Terms of Service, TikTok Terms of Service, and acknowledge that you have read the TikTok Privacy Policy for partners to understand how we collect, use, and share your data. You can use the same login information to access the Business Center and TikTok Ads Manager. In addition, you will be able to use the revenue of your store to pay for advertising metrics.
login.continue_login_2: You also agree that your products will be automatically added to the Open Collaboration program, with a product category-based commission rate.

about.description: TikTok-Booking is a global online travel agency and metasearch engine with a significant international presence. Founded in 2012, alongside its headquarters in Brno, Czech Republic, TikTok-Booking has established branches and offices in various locations worldwide, allowing it to cater to travelers across the globe.
about.description_2: The company operates in multiple continents, including Europe, North America, Asia, and Oceania. It has strategically positioned branches and offices in key cities such as London (United Kingdom), Barcelona (Spain), Miami (United States), Sydney (Australia), and Singapore. This global footprint enables TikTok-Booking to provide localized services, support, and expertise to customers in different regions.
about.description_3: In terms of marketing, TikTok-Booking employs various strategies to reach and engage its target audience. The company invests in digital marketing channels such as search engine advertising, social media campaigns, and email marketing to raise brand awareness and promote its services.
about.description_4: Additionally, TikTok-Booking collaborates with influencers and travel bloggers to showcase its offerings and generate buzz among potential travelers.
about.description_5: TikTok-Booking also utilizes affiliate marketing programs, partnering with relevant websites and platforms to expand its reach and attract more customers. By offering attractive commissions and incentives, TikTok-Booking incentivizes affiliates to promote its services and drive bookings.
about.description_6: Furthermore, TikTok-Booking implements customer loyalty programs and referral schemes to encourage repeat business and word-of-mouth marketing. Through these initiatives, satisfied customers are rewarded for their loyalty and incentivized to refer their friends and family to use TikTok-Booking for their travel needs.

team.commission_2: The commission earned from the agent will be automatically added to your account or displayed in the team report.
team.description_2: It is important to note that all agents and their agents have the opportunity to earn money and receive a certain percentage of the commission.
team.description_3: Profit, that is, 25% of the commission of the agent below, will not affect the agent and the agent below who are actively building their team.
team.description_4: The system operates in a transparent and fair system, encouraging agents and their agents to strive and maximize their profits.
team.description_5: By expanding their network and nurturing the success of their agent below, the agent can benefit from a sustainable business model and profits.
